Usage Examples


--------------




--------------




--------------




--------------




--------------






Basic Validation

























.. code-block:: python

      validator = InputValidator()
      if validator.validate_video("video.mp4"):
         print("Video is valid")




Advanced Processing

























.. code-block:: python

      processor = InputProcessor(config)
      result = processor.process_video(
         "video.mp4",
         target_format='mp4',
         target_fps=30
      )

